author: Unreal Engine
description:
Luxury real estate developer DAMAC Properties aimed to offer buyers an immersive real-time experience. PropVR provided an engaging digital twin framework, contributing to DAMAC increasing property revenues from $24 million to $400 million.

Read our interview with PropVR to learn more about this project: https://www.unrealengine.com/en-US/feed

#digitaltwin #realestate #unrealengine #ue5
title: PropVR’s digital twins help real estate developer boost revenue by 10x
